====Noun====
{{en-noun}}
# A [[sudden]], [[vigorous]] [[pull]] (sometimes defined as mass times [[jerk]], or rate of change of [[force]]).
#: {{ux|en|He unjammed the rope with a short '''yank'''.}}
# {{lb|en|slang}} A [[masturbation]] session.
#* {{quote-book|en|2012|Bonnie Dee, Summer Devon|Serious Play|page=81|text=He rested his hand on his bare chest, an innocent enough spot, but soon it drifted of its own accord down his stomach to slide beneath the waistband of his briefs. Fine. A quick '''yank''' would relieve the sexual tension that simmered in him.}}
